---
title: Cheesy Creamy Cauliflower and Chicken Pasta with Baby Spinach
description: Making the perfect mac 'n’ cheese starts with a velvety cheddar cheese sauce and a swirl of cream. Roasted cauliflower, chicken and a sprinkle of chili flakes add elegance to this everyday favourite!
